SimonShield
===========
A simple Arduino shield to build a Simon game.

Directories:
============
|
+-Laser	                - Design files of the laser cut bottom plate
|
+-KiCad			- KiCad project file, schematic, layout, and libraries
|
+-Gerber                - Gerber files for manufacturing


Files:
======
|
+-SimonShield-RevA Schematic.pdf      - Schematic
|
+-SimonShield-RevA BOM.txt            - Bill of materials
|
+-SimonShield-RevA Assembly Plan.pdf  - Shows the location of all components
                                      to be assembled


